    region span-style-font-size-1-2em-font-weight-400-all-workshops-sprints-span (
        name: <span style="font-size: 1.2em; font-weight: 400">All Workshops & Sprints</span>
        type: staticContent
        source {
            htmlCode:
                ```html
                <table><tr><td width="120px">
                <img src="https://c4u04.objectstorage.us-ashburn-1.oci.customer-oci.com/p/cBQqSkJksuZca_VCqfZ2uP2Tvgqafe3eBya0I-EtOKAJ77uF0nN-ygNzr4bcL8QO/n/c4u04/b/logos/o/william_wms_biglogo.png" width="100px">
                </td><td>
                <p>All workshops WMS are listed below.  You can customize the report to your liking and save it for your next session. We also have several canned reports saved for you.<br><strong>To access all the columns or presaved reports:</strong><br>1. Click Actions -> Columns.  <br>2. You can filter, download as an excel, convert to a chart and more in the actions menu.<br><strong>To subscribe and get this report emailed to you monthly or weekly:</strong> <br>1. Click Actions -> Subscription<br>2. Enter your email, subject and frequency<br>3. Click apply<br><strong>To download:</strong> <br>1. Click Actions -> Download<br>2. Choose your report format<br></p></td></tr></table> 
                ```
        }
